    ( 9, 0): H ∈ [19], expected 1+2·9+4·0 = 19 ✓
    ( 9, 1): H ∈ [23], expected 1+2·9+4·1 = 23 ✓
    (11, 0): H ∈ [23], expected 1+2·11+4·0 = 23 ✓
    (11, 1): H ∈ [27], expected 1+2·11+4·1 = 27 ✓
    (12, 0): H ∈ [25], expected 1+2·12+4·0 = 25 ✓
